{"word":"G5602 - ὧδε - hōde - ho'-deh - Here","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὧδε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hōde</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ho'-deh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Here</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இங்கே, இவ்விடத்தில் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. so, in this manner"},{"paragraph":"2. in this place"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>h<b>o&#x0304;de</b> - <i>ho'-deh</i><p/>From an adverb form of <a href=\"#/G3592 - ὅδε - hóde - hod'-eh/3592\">G3592</a>; <i>in this</i> same spot, that is, <i>here</i> or <i>hither:</i> - here, hither, (in) this place, there.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}